。相当于test（），这个时候this就是window。故这样调用的函数this就是指的window，故window.name=The Window.</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"><span cm-text="">​</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">//代码片段二</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-comment">//对于片段一我们的本意是不是想输出My Object。那么怎么改造，通过that=this去操作，这样子</span></span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">name2</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-string">"The Window"</span>;</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">object2</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> {</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">name2</span>: <span class="cm-string">"My Object"</span>,</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-property">getNameFunc</span>: <span class="cm-keyword">function</span> () {</span></pre><pre class=" CodeMirror-line " role="presentation"><span role="presentation" style="padding-right: 0.1px;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class="cm-keyword">var</span> <span class="cm-def">that</span> <span class="cm-operator">=</span> <span class="cm-keyword">this</span>;</span></pre><p